casebody.data:
STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Kurt Alan OLSON, Defendant-Appellant. No. 17-1872 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed April 3, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Kurt Alan Olson appeals from his convictions for two counts of indecent contact with a child and three counts of assault with intent to commit sexual abuse. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
